OL,3,CPublic to decide asylum cases as
OL,4,CMahmood pledges to speed up decisions
OL,6,FMembers of the public will be trained
OL,7,Fto decide asylum appeals instead of
OL,8,Fimmigration judges under reforms to
OL,9,Fspeed up outcomes as Shabana Mahmood
OL,10,Fpledged the removal of 45,000 failed
OL,11,Fclaimants and foreign offenders.
OL,13,FThe Home Secretary will set out plans
OL,14,Ffor a new independent body which
OL,15,Fofficials say will prioritise cases in
OL,16,Fthe public interest and high-harm
OL,17,Foffenders starting from late 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
