OL,3,CPublic to decide asylum cases as
OL,4,CMahmood pledges to speed up decisions
OL,6,FThe Independent Immigration Appeals
OL,7,FAuthority will be made up of
OL,8,F"professionally trained and
OL,9,Findependently appointed" adjudicators
OL,10,Ffrom a range of backgrounds, similar
OL,11,Fto magistrates.
OL,13,FThe Government hopes that broadening
OL,14,Fthe eligibility criteria will allow
OL,15,Ffor a significant increase in capacity
OL,16,Fand lead to faster outcomes.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@XO]
