OL,3,CPublic to decide asylum cases as
OL,4,CMahmood pledges to speed up decisions
OL,6,FThe reforms, to be laid out in the
OL,7,FImmigration and Asylum Bill this week,
OL,8,Fwill also seek to create a "single
OL,9,Froute" that prevents migrants from
OL,10,Fappealing against a rejected claim and
OL,11,Fbringing further claims about new
OL,12,Fmatters before their removal.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the Home Office said
OL,15,Fexpansions to two immigration removal
OL,16,Fcentres would help to ensure the
OL,17,Fremoval of more than 45,000 people
OL,18,Ffound to have no right to stay in the
OL,19,FUK.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@FO]
