OL,3,CPublic to decide asylum cases as
OL,4,CMahmood pledges to speed up decisions
OL,6,F"Our new appeals body will ensure
OL,7,Fclaims are heard swiftly and fairly.
OL,8,FThose with a legitimate claim will get
OL,9,Ftheir hearing. Those who have no right
OL,10,Fto remain in this country, and are
OL,11,Fabusing the system, will be swiftly
OL,12,Fremoved."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]
